Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.69,0:00:06.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:10.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.73,0:00:12.44,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.44,0:00:14.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.07,0:00:15.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu isn't with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:17.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:21.29,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,He was hospitalized after catching\Nthe flu at the end of the year,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.91,0:00:24.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,and he's been home in bed\Never since he got discharged.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:27.21,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That sounds serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.21,0:00:28.88,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,We should go check up on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:30.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.17,0:00:35.34,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.88,0:00:37.22,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.18,0:00:42.02,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,(My Silky Love)\NEvery time I think of you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.18,0:00:42.02,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,MY SILKY LOVE nijuu yojikan zutto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:45.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,(My Silky Love)\Nfor 24 hours straight,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:45.52,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,MY SILKY LOVE kimino koto omoutabi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:49.11,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,(My Silky Love)\NIt only makes me feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:49.11,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,MY SILKY LOVE modokashii kono kimochi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:53.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,(My Silky Love)\Nthat much more impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:53.03,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,MY SILKY LOVE tada afure kaetteku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:59.99,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so simple just to say I love you.\NBut when you come close to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:59.99,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,sukito ieba kantan nanoni\Nkimiga maeni kichauto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.99,0:01:06.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,my own emotions go awry\Nand get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.99,0:01:06.96,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,kyaraga sobie watashino\Nkoto wo jamashiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:14.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I can bring myself to do anything.\NThat's who I'm supposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:14.63,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,itsumonaraba tsuyoki de ikeru\Nsonna seikakunanoni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.63,0:01:20.89,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But I just can't break this\Nwall down no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.63,0:01:20.89,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,donna ganbatte mitemo kabewa kuzusenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.89,0:01:24.43,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Please understand these feelings for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.89,0:01:24.43,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,sasshite hoshii kono kimoch iwo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:27.94,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why these gazes of mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:27.94,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,dakara watashi wa itsumo kimini
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:31.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,they tell my love for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:31.57,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,daisuki dayoto okuru shisen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.57,0:01:35.61,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Now gather up my courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.57,0:01:35.61,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,saidaino yuukide
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.61,0:01:39.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,A fragile heart made of silk,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.61,0:01:39.16,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,yabure souna shirukuno haato
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:42.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized that by meeting you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:42.66,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,kimini atte kizuita yatto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:48.37,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so clumsy when it comes to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:48.37,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,ainiwa bukiyou dattan datte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.71,0:01:53.13,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,A forgotten scar left in my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.71,0:01:53.13,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,wasure kaketa koino kizuato
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:56.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,and I suddenly felt it sting deep inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:56.76,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,kyuuni uzuki dashitano kyunto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:02:01.18,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to say that I love you someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:02:01.18,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,itsukawa watashi rashiku sukito iwanakya
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:06.02,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Or it'll keep making me weaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:06.02,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,imayori yowaku nacchauyo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:15.32,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay Like This Forever
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:15.32,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up bedridden all winter break...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.19,0:02:19.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to face her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:21.82,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:24.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,shot down, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:26.75,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather definitively.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:29.42,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:35.30,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why are you ignoring me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:36.51,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:37.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tai—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:41.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:42.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it down, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:43.85,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,My noodles are going to get soggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:45.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Eating that junk again...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:49.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So annoying. Maybe I'll eat it in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:50.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ready now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:57.94,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I've still been cooking\Nyour share every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:03:01.53,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,so why haven't you come\Nover since New Year's?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:04.47,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, I know you're upset about Minorin rejecting you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but don't take it out on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:08.75,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:10.37,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:13.33,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not asking for your pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:16.34,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But you could at least act normal around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:18.42,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,This is for you and Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:22.34,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:25.82,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'd help you with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:27.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,but I spent all my time at your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:31.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder she got the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:35.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And you think that's why she shot me down?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:37.32,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:41.24,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty sure she just isn't attracted to me—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:44.99,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm positive Minorin likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:48.29,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But she believes that {\i1}I{\i0} need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:53.92,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you honestly think Minorin\Ndoesn't like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:56.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:04:02.97,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I sorta had this feeling that\Nshe was kinda interested in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:04.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Then don't avoid her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:08.85,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't go over to your place anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:10.43,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need you to make me food.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:11.89,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And you don't have to wake\Nme up in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:14.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,If I learn to survive on my own,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:18.11,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,and your feelings for Minorin don't change,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:21.15,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she'll respond differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:23.11,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:26.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:29.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You should do what you need to!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:31.25,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:34.50,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Find out how Minorin truly feels!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:37.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:42.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But try not to burn the place down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:46.18,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I promise to never use the stove.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:48.30,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear to eat out for the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:50.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:52.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to last?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:58.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:04:59.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:01.23,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:03.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:08.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't run away, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:12.41,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:16.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu-chan, you forgot something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:19.34,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, I signed it for you and everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:20.75,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Signed what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:23.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The Okinawa thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:24.47,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Consent Form
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:24.47,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:25.92,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Close one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:27.84,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I totally forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:30.43,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to Okinawa for your class trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:32.81,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so wonderful! How fancy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:34.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:36.89,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinda got bigger issues on my\Nmind right now, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:39.69,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:48.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I see Kushieda, I'll go up and say hi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:50.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll start from there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:52.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:58.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to return this as soon as possible.\NIt looked really expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:01.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:03.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're that costume guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:04.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:06.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I completely forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:08.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:10.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:13.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,This was in the pocket the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:18.23,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:23.02,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't actually need it that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:26.94,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Beach! Sun! Okinawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:29.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Pit vipers! Biscuits! Okinawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:31.20,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Six days and five nights in Okinawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:32.37,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Woo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:35.08,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Tiger! Happy New Year and all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:36.91,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:39.08,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unusual. Where's Taka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:40.50,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:43.75,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:46.30,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiger! Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:48.22,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here! Read this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:48.22,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Souvenirs from Okinawa:\NBiscuit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:50.97,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Bi-Bigstick. {tl:penis joke}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:54.18,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys hear that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:01.77,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Too late for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:03.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Whoa! Hey!\N- Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:06.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Taka-chan! Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:07.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiger kicked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:09.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you kept moaning about biscuits!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:11.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.53,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:15.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:16.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:18.12,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What's it called...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:20.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Something I no longer need.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:21.83,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoink!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:24.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? How's it look?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:25.50,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Give that back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:27.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:29.47,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That still belongs to Ryuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:32.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- You're gonna make me bald... Ow!\N- Give it back to him right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:33.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:35.43,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Good to see everyone's excited\Nfor the new semester!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:37.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, people!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:39.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,'Sup?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:41.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:42.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:43.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,G—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:46.32,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,G...Go—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:49.23,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta go buy juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:51.95,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Class is about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:53.20,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:57.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:58.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such a dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:04.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish everything would burn to the ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:07.50,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It burned to the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:10.84,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But nothing will be canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:12.84,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So everything's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:14.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,All will go as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:17.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach, we have no idea what\Nyou're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:22.23,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The hotel we were going to stay at\Nin Okinawa burned down in a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:25.85,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, we'll be having a three-day,\Ntwo-night ski trip in the mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:27.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Isn't that great?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:29.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:31.53,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:33.74,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame me! I didn't burn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:34.70,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I strongly object!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:35.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:36.24,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:39.37,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does Ami-chan have to\Nbe late when we need her!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:42.12,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she could do something about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:44.92,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawashima-san is working in Hawaii.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:47.38,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to flight issues, she\Nwon't make it back today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:51.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And since she's spent plenty\Nof time on tropical islands,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:53.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,she might actually prefer a\Nwinter mountain excursion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:55.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:55.84,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,This is torture!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:59.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- My first plane ride! My first Okinawa trip!\N- Who goes to the mountains during winter!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:01.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You single...thirty-something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:08.36,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Life doesn't always go your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:12.90,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:14.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:15.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:17.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Aisaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:18.53,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,She isn't with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:20.28,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:22.62,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she had something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:24.79,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I learn to survive on my own,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:28.50,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and your feelings for Minorin don't change...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:32.59,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's living on cup noodles\Nto help me, and I'm...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:36.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:36.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:47.65,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:50.31,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,She was gorgeous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:51.65,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's a model?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:57.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:01.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were working in Hawaii.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:02.95,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:04.33,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Piss off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:05.69,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you picking a fight
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when we haven't seen each other since before break?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:10.13,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:11.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:14.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,She called you an idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:16.88,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:18.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Why are you—?\N- You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:21.51,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,We were supposed to meet ten minutes ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.51,0:10:24.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so anal, Dumb-chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:29.44,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:30.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,As requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:33.02,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:37.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are close enough to\Nbuy gifts for each other now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:38.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:40.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:44.70,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad I don't need it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:47.33,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well. It'll have its uses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:49.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you taking it to Okinawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:52.13,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:55.25,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been changed to a\Nthree-day, two-night ski trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:56.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:58.84,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Our hotel in Okinawa burned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:01.14,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:02.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:05.89,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:06.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:08.27,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:12.15,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to tell you before we leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:13.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:16.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hang around Ryuji on the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:17.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:21.24,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's{\i0} the one always hanging around {\i1}me{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:22.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:25.33,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin shot Ryuji down on Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:26.83,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:29.97,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,More like, she implied that I shouldn't tell her
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my feelings before I even got the chance to!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:34.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:36.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So somebody finally got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:38.34,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:41.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin's actually attracted to Ryuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:45.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just not working out for various reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:47.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,When we're seniors,\Nwe'll have college exams,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:49.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,not to mention we might end\Nup in different classes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:54.27,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So this trip is our last chance to\Nfind out how Minorin truly feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:57.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it, Dumb-chi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:01.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you really want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:06.91,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, what a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:08.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:10.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:18.84,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame that you're not\Nthe only one who got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:21.34,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:23.59,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess you're too stupid to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:29.18,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:39.65,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why are you following me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:42.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I happen to be headed this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:47.28,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:51.79,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize you were so serious\Nabout Kushieda and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:54.29,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:57.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:13:00.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do what I can on the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:05.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if there's no point in finding\Nout how Kushieda feels, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:06.84,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:09.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Your feelings are mutual.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:12.35,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Trust me. It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:13.89,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:18.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so confident?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:19.77,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Really wanna know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:25.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I have good reason\Nto believe that it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.16,0:13:29.33,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm saying is, I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:33.58,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that you're worthy of Minorin's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:37.79,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I need to drop by the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:41.42,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,A new shop opened\Nthat sells boxed lunches.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:42.50,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:44.85,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait. What was up with\Nyour attitude today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:48.18,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You better not avoid her again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:49.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:54.77,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Taiga believes in me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:58.82,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't take the next step,\Nit's like I'm disappointing her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:02.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.94,0:14:08.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Yoyo Ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:08.99,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:12.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry about yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:13.91,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:16.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Whatcha talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:18.29,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't bother me one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:21.42,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:24.21,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll go, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:26.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:32.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't no thang!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:34.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:35.35,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Tai—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:37.98,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You were caught, so you get to carry my stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:43.27,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:47.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Stupid Taiga, stupid Taiga, stupid Taiga...\N- Kushieda...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:52.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, this is no big deal!\NNo problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:54.37,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, give me a handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:03.50,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:05.13,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hair looks a little different.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:06.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:08.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a little trim.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:12.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually wanted to cut it super short.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:15.51,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a guy's.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:21.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a buzz cut back in grade school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:24.11,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd sit next to my little brother at the barber's,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:25.94,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,and they'd just zip my hair\Noff with the clippers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:29.70,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,My nickname was Mr. Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:31.95,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I'm surprised you noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:33.91,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:35.62,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I spend a lot of time looking at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:40.12,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, now there's a shocking confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:41.12,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:43.62,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah, I have to take the next step.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:46.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:48.21,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Your brother plays high\Nschool baseball, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:51.13,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,His school regularly makes it to nationals.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:53.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you must be proud of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.64,0:15:56.35,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh. But to be honest,\NI'm jealous of him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:57.43,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:00.14,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Amin-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:01.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,First time I've seen you this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:05.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, good morning, Minori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:07.11,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:09.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, sure haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:11.32,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I say...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:13.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,This makes me sigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:15.12,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:16.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:18.37,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:19.90,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Whyever would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:24.29,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:26.92,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,These will be the groups for the trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:28.38,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:30.59,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think they're a little weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:33.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You, Ami, and Kashii.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:34.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka and Kushieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:36.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu and Noto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:37.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruta and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:39.31,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,A mixed group of nine boys and girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:41.65,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Since our class has more girls than boys,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.65,0:16:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this arrangement seems perfect to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:47.23,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But this means you and Tiger...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:48.27,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:49.69,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But this means...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:50.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:53.20,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Join another group if you've got a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:54.74,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a pain in the ass, Noto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:56.41,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:58.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I said you're being a pain in the ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:00.20,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Any thoughts, Takasu?\N- You're a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:02.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:03.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Takasu-kun agrees!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:08.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- If you have a problem, join a different grou—\N- I said that's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:09.84,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Professor Kitamura agrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:11.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You can stop talking, Noto!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:13.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you being so mean!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:17.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? We have to make a guide?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:17.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:21.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Each team has to write one up\Nand turn it in by next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:23.18,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to waste our time on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:25.94,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we all meet up someplace\Nto work on it together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:27.23,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But where?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:29.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,How about my place on Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:31.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:33.11,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh, it's pretty big.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.45,0:17:36.24,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:38.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This place is unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:40.58,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how much the rent is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:41.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Takasu are neighbors, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:44.25,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Takasu-kun lives in this building too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:46.71,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm in the place next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:49.13,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:49.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:55.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I borrowed some examples from\Nprevious trips to use as reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:57.38,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be some guides in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:17:58.97,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:17:59.89,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:01.85,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go make some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:04.18,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought madeleines.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:07.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka, where can I find an outlet\Nto plug in my computer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:08.23,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.77,0:18:09.94,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:14.15,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You can act normal around Kitamura now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:15.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,More or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:18.70,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about that. Go help Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:20.20,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:23.91,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:25.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me give you a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:26.83,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Golgo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:28.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not Golgo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:30.79,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm Golgo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:32.92,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stand behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:34.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I'm standing behind you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:36.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:43.14,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels so weird to see clean\Ndishes at Taiga's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:47.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been here in a year.\NEverything looks totally different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:50.77,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:55.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I haven't done anything lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:57.15,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga's been doing this by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:19:01.62,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're still the reason she can do it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:02.74,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:07.77,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Ouch, burning...\N- You haven't visited in a year?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:09.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:11.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,After the stuff with her dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:16.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought if I stopped coming over and gave us some space,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.16,0:19:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't mess up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:20.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.47,0:19:22.97,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You did a good job, Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:26.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You stepped in here and didn't let yourself\Nget worked up about screwing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:28.85,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:33.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you think anybody will notice\Nif we copy the whole thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:37.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would we copy a guide to Okinawa\Nwhen we're headed for snowy mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:38.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:43.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:46.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:49.75,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let Yusaku see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:51.21,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey, Ami-chan!\N- What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:53.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're better off not knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:56.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That only makes me more curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:19:58.13,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:20:00.47,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be a shock, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:03.34,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a picture, but after\Nthat grand rejection—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:04.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! Stupid! Stupid! Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:05.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Dumb-chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:06.35,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:08.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- It's his fault for being so sensitive!\N- Here you go! Tea's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:10.81,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- What was that!?\N- Man, could you two get along?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:17.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To be honest, I'm kinda looking\Nforward to the class trip.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:23.28,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because it's the last time 2-C\Nwill get to do something together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:27.24,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This class has been so much fun...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:28.79,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to miss it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:33.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If only we could stay like this forever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:35.62,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah, you're right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:37.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If only we could stay like this forever...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:42.27,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can Kushieda and I...and everyone else...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:44.47,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}stay like this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:51.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,She sorted her trash...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:00.44,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:03.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We can't stay like this forever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:09.70,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to use this trip to find\Nout how Kushieda truly feels.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:12.16,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Bus #3\NOhashi High School
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.89,0:21:13.21,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-S-Sour grapes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.21,0:21:16.21,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-S-Silver oxide battery.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:17.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yucky scab.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:19.25,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Belly button lint from a maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:21.51,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:25.13,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu, we're on "E."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:26.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Every effort counts!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:28.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:31.18,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You can only use things that are bitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:35.89,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you could say that\Nwasted effort is a bitter thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:37.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a point there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.90,0:21:39.44,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we're on to "T."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:39.94,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,T...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:42.44,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,T-T-T...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.44,0:21:44.70,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-ta-ta-ta...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.70,0:21:46.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- As in, Bobby Bitter singing scat.\N- {\i1}Yeah...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:48.33,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Who the hell is that!?\N- {\i1}Every little effort counts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.78,0:21:53.41,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I'll try one more time to express the\Nfeelings she denied on Christmas Eve.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:11.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,In those sleepless nights,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:11.72,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,nemurenai yoruni wa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:14.98,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I lay there sighing all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:14.98,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,hitoride tameiki
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.48,0:22:18.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What about everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.48,0:22:18.60,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,minna wa dounano
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:22.32,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It just feels so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:22.32,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,nandaka samishii
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.32,0:22:28.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,A tiny little seed in this huge Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.32,0:22:28.86,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,hiroi daichini hitotsubu no tane
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.57,0:22:32.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Stretch out those roots,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.57,0:22:32.03,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,nekko nobashite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.03,0:22:39.75,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,and bear a fruit that's still unripe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.03,0:22:39.75,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,mada aoi miwo tsuketa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.75,0:22:44.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The fruit that wants to hurry and turn orange.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.75,0:22:44.63,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,orenji ironi hayaku naritai kajitsu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.63,0:22:47.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Showering in your light
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.63,0:22:47.93,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,kimino hikari wo abite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.93,0:22:51.47,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,only nurtures bigger ideals and dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.93,0:22:51.47,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,risou ya yume wa fukuramu bakari
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.47,0:22:54.85,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.47,0:22:54.85,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,kizuiteyo nee
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:23:01.65,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I ate the orange today but cried\Nbecause it was still too sour.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:23:01.65,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,orenji kyoumo tabete mitakedo\Nmada suppakute naita
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.81,0:23:05.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It reminded too much of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.81,0:23:05.19,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,watashi mitaide nokosenai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.19,0:23:07.61,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,so I finished the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.19,0:23:07.61,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,zenbu tabeta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:14.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you. It makes me cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:14.16,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,sukidayo nakeruyo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:21.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you. I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:21.04,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,sukidayo sukidayo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:34.97,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't Help Myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.46,0:23:27.51,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to redo my\NChristmas Eve confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.51,0:23:29.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just for me, but for Taiga and\Nall the support she's given me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:31.51,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.51,0:23:33.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,All talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.05,0:23:34.25,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take this anymore.
